TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STORES.STORE_NUM, STORES.STORENAME, STORES.LOCATION, STORES.MANAGER, STORES.LASTMODIFIED FROM STORES where STORES.LASTMODIFIED > TO_DATE( '$$V_LASTRUN' , 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS' )

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( NOT ISNULL(LKP_STOREID) AND LKP_MANAGER != MANAGER , 'TRUE', 'FALSE' )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: UPDATE_REC

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DIMSTORES.SURROGATEKEY as SURROGATEKEY, DIMSTORES.STORENAME as STORENAME, DIMSTORES.LOCATION as LOCATION, DIMSTORES.MANAGER as MANAGER, DIMSTORES.STARTDATE as STARTDATE, DIMSTORES.ENDDATE as ENDDATE, DIMSTORES.CHGE_CURRENT_IND as CHGE_CURRENT_IND, DIMSTORES.LASTMODIFIED as LASTMODIFIED, DIMSTORES.STOREID as STOREID FROM DIMSTORES WHERE CHGE_CURRENT_IND = 'Y'

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1
